commit.message:
Updating maven-javadoc-pugin to 3.2.0

Signed-off-by: Maxim Nesen <maxim.nesen@oracle.com>

Rest client update to version 1.4.1

Signed-off-by: David Kral <david.k.kral@oracle.com>

Allow for specifying Feature processing order

Signed-off-by: jansupol <jan.supol@oracle.com>

Bump ant from 1.10.7 to 1.10.8

Bumps ant from 1.10.7 to 1.10.8.

Signed-off-by: dependabot[bot] <support@github.com>

updateing dependencies versions

Signed-off-by: Maxim Nesen <maxim.nesen@oracle.com>

JAX-RS link fixes (new apidocs location)

Signed-off-by: Maxim Nesen <maxim.nesen@oracle.com>

Allow concurrent CompletionException & ExecutionException to be unwrapped for the ExceptionMapper

Signed-off-by: jansupol <jan.supol@oracle.com>

Updated HK2 info in the migration guide

Signed-off-by: jansupol <jan.supol@oracle.com>

Response.hasEntity to return true if buffered after readEntity

Signed-off-by: jansupol <jan.supol@oracle.com>

RestClientListener call switched

Signed-off-by: David Kral <david.k.kral@oracle.com>

year update

Signed-off-by: David Kral <david.k.kral@oracle.com>

Use Helidon Connector from Helidon (#4569)

* Use Helidon Connector from Helidon

Signed-off-by: jansupol <jan.supol@oracle.com>

Fix issue with optional CDI in BV module (#4574)

Fixes #4542

Signed-off-by: jansupol <jan.supol@oracle.com>

Prevent race condition
Fixes 4493

Signed-off-by: jansupol <jan.supol@oracle.com>

SSE Flow.Subscriber injectable as event sink

  * Java Flow api used only by JerseyEventSink in java 11+
  * Reactive streams tck tests for JerseyEventSink
  * Cancel on close propagation
  * Remove tests contradicting reactive streams spec https://github.com/reactive-streams/reactive-streams-jvm#2.13

Signed-off-by: Daniel Kec <daniel.kec@oracle.com>

Support TLSv1.3 (#4528)

* Support TLSv 1.3

Signed-off-by: Jorge Bescos Gascon <jorge.bescos.gascon@oracle.com>

TimeOut property for Netty Connector
MaxConnections for Netty Connector
MaxConnectionsTotal for NettyConnector

Fixes #4548

Signed-off-by: jansupol <jan.supol@oracle.com>

Implement ExecutionStatisticsDynamicBean.getAttributes

Implementation was missing. Needed in order to use this bean with generic JMX collector from Prometheus: https://github.com/prometheus/jmx_exporter.

Signed-off-by: Trond Marius Øvstetun <trond@ovstetun.no>

Expect:100-Continue header handling

Signed-off-by: Maxim Nesen <maxim.nesen@oracle.com>

HTTP 100-Continue handling arranged

Signed-off-by: Maxim Nesen <maxim.nesen@oracle.com>

resolve properties fix

Signed-off-by: Maxim Nesen <maxim.nesen@oracle.com>

attributeValue NPE handling

Signed-off-by: Maxim Nesen <maxim.nesen@oracle.com>

Put Helidon Properties file back

Signed-off-by: jansupol <jan.supol@oracle.com>

Support Apache HttpEntity as an entity type when using Apache Connector

Signed-off-by: jansupol <jan.supol@oracle.com>

Update Copyright year

Signed-off-by: jansupol <jan.supol@oracle.com>

Add Helidon module to bom pom and remove Jackson 1 (#4582)

* Add Helidon module to bom pom and remove Jackson 1

Signed-off-by: jansupol <jan.supol@oracle.com>
2.33-SNAPSHOT

Merge pull request #4583 from eclipse-ee4j/2.32-BRANCH

Technical merge of released branch 2.32-BRANCH

Merge remote-tracking branch 'upstream/master' into 3.x_merged

Signed-off-by: Maxim Nesen <maxim.nesen@oracle.com>

Jakartification fixes

Signed-off-by: Maxim Nesen <maxim.nesen@oracle.com>
